Package: gflow
Title: Gradient Flow Data Analysis Framework
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Pawel", "Gajer", , "pgajer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools and methods for gradient flow data analysis
    framework. The package implements various algorithms for graph construction,
    path analysis, and gradient flow computation, facilitating the exploration
    and understanding of high-dimensional data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
